records.name: Dhawa Ihuru, Part Of Banyan Group

location.address: Male City, North Male Atoll, 08300 Male

descriptions.direction: Located in Ihuru, Dhawa Ihuru, part of Banyan Group is on the beach. Orofini Jewellery and Boutique by Island Breeze are worth checking out if shopping is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Full Moon Beach and Paradise Island Beach. Gili Lankanfushi Beach and Kurumba Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Looking to get your feet wet? Windsurfing and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Relax at the eco-friendly beachfront villas of the Angsana Ihuru resort. Each villa has a private patio with dining area and a Maldivian swing, and some feature an open-air jet pool. All have in-room Wi-Fi. The resort offers guided snorkelling safaris, Maldivian cooking classes and a 5-star PADI dive centre. Guests can relax with massages and aromatherapy at the award-winning spa or enjoy a stroll on the white sandy beach. The well-equipped water sports centre offers non-motorised sports equipment free of charge. Angsana Ihuru Resort is located in the North Malé Atoll, a 20-minute speedboat ride from Malé International Airport.
